# fix(auth): prevent token refresh race condition
#
# Root cause: Multiple concurrent requests could attempt token refresh
# simultaneously, causing authentication failures.
#
# Solution: Add mutex lock around token refresh logic to ensure only
# one refresh operation occurs at a time.
#
# Impact: Fixes ~5% of authentication errors in production.
#
# Fixes: GH-234
